<div><p style="font-size:18pt; line-height:150%; margin:15.6pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体; font-size:18pt; font-weight:bold">国家学生体质健康标准（</span><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体; font-size:18pt; font-weight:bold">2014</span><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体; font-size:18pt; font-weight:bold">年修订）</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:20.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">一、说明</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">1.</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">《国家学生体质健康标准》（以下简称《标准》）是国家学校教育工作的基础性指导文件和教育质量基本标准，是评价学生综合素质、评估学校工作和衡量各地教育发展的重要依据，是《国家体育锻炼标准》在学校的具体实施，适用于全日制普通小学、初中、普通高中、中等职业学校、普通高等学校的学生。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">2.</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">本标准的修订坚持健康第一，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">落实</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">《国家中长期教育改革和发展规划纲要（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">2010-2020</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">年）》、《国务院办公厅转发教育部等部门关于进一步加强学校体育工作若干意见的通知》（国办发〔</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">2012</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">〕</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">53</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">号）和《教育部关于印发〈学生体质健康监测评价办法〉等三个文件的通知》（教体艺〔</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">2014</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">〕</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">号）有关要求，着重提高《标准》应用的信度、效度和区分度，着重强化其教育激励、反馈调整和引导锻炼的功能，着重提高其教育监测和绩效评价的支撑能力。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">3.</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">本标准从身体形态、身体机能和身体素质等方面综合评定学生的体质健康水平，是促进学生体质健康发展、激励学生积极进行身体锻</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">炼的教育手段，是国家学生发展核心素养体系和学业质量标准的重要组成部分，是学生体质健康的个体评价标准。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">4.</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">本标准将适用对象划分为以下组别：小学、初中、高中按每个年级为一组，其中小学为</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">组、初中为</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">组、高中</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">为</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">组。大学一、二年级为一组，三、四年级为一组。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．小学、初中、高中、大学各组别的测试指标均为必测指标。其中，身体形态类中的身高、体重，身体机能类中的肺活量，以及身体素质类中的</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">50</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">米跑、坐位体前屈为各年级学生共性指标。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">6</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．本标准的学年总分由标准分与附加分之和构成，满分为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">120</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分。标准分由各单项指标得分与</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">权重乘积之和组成，满分为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">100</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分。附加分根据实测成绩确定，即对成绩超过</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">100</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分的加分指标进行加分，满分为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">20</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分；小学的加分指标为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">1</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分钟跳绳，加分幅度为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">20</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分；初中、高中和大学的加分指标为男生引体向上和</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">1000</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">米跑，女生</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">1</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分钟仰卧起坐和</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">800</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">米跑，各指标加分幅度均为</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">10</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分。</span></p><p style="line-height:26pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">7</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．根据学生学年总分评定等级：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">90.0</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分及以上为优秀，</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">80.0</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">～</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">89.9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分为良好，</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">60.0</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">～</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">79.9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分为及格，</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">59.9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分及以下为不及格。</span></p><p style="line-height:26pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">8</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．每个学生每学年评定一次，记入《〈国家学生体质健康标准〉登记卡》（附表</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">1</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">～</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">6</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">）。</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">特殊学制的学校，在</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">填写登记卡时可以按规定和需求相应地增减栏目。</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">学生毕业时的成绩和等级，按毕业当年学年总分的</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">50%</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">与其他学年总分平均得分的</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">50%</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">之和进行评定。</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:31.5pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．学生测试成绩评定达到良好及以上者，方可参加评优与评奖；成绩达到优秀者，方可获体育奖学分。</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">测试成绩评定不及格者，在本学年度准予补测一次，补测仍不及格，则学年成绩评定为不及格。普通高中、中等职业学校和普通高等学校学生毕业时，《标准》测试的成绩达不到</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">50</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">分者按结</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">业或肄业处理。</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">10</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．学生因病或残疾可向学校提交暂缓或免予执行《标准》的申请，经医疗单位证明，体育教学部门核准，可暂缓或免予执行《标准》，并填写《免予执行</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">&lt;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">国家学生体质健康标准</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">&gt;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">申请表》</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">（附表</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">7</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">）</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">，存入学生档案。确实丧失运动能力、被免予执行《标准》的残疾学生，仍可参加评优与评奖，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">毕业时《标准》成绩需注明免测。</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">11</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">各学校每学年开展覆盖本校各年级学生的《标准》测试工作，《标准》测试数据经当地教育行政部门按要求审核后，通过“中国学生体质健康网”上传至“国家学生体质健康标准数据管理系统”。测试和数据上传时间由教育行政部门确定。</span></p><p style="line-height:26pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">12</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">．本标准由教育部负责解释。</span></p><br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both" /><p style="margin:0pt; text-indent:21pt"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:16pt">二、单项指标与权重</span></p><div style="text-align:center"><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin:0 auto; width:438.15pt"><tr style="height:22.7pt"><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; font-size:12pt">%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">）</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:22.7pt"><td rowspan="2" style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; font-size:12pt">小学一年级至大学四年级</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; padding-left:5.03pt; padding-right:5.03pt; vertical-align:top; width:191.3pt"><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">体重指数（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">BMI</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">）</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; width:52.2pt"><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">15</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:22.7pt"><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; padding-left:5.03pt; padding-right:5.03pt; vertical-align:top; width:191.3pt"><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">肺活量</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; padding-left:5.03pt; padding-right:5.03pt; vertical-align:top; width:52.2pt"><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">15</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:22.7pt"><td rowspan="3" style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.75pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.75pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.75pt; padding-left:5.03pt; padding-right:5.03pt; vertical-align:middle; width:161.5pt"><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">小学一、二年级</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.75pt;
